I was just boarding a train in a subway station when it started. The doors closed and everyone was fairly calm until it started getting worse. When the locals look nervous you know something is wrong. After what seemed an age the doors opened and people streamed off of train and towards the exit. No one ran - but we did all walk at a brisk pace.



